data.description: MOVE right in and ENJOY country living at its best!! FEEL the peace and Serenity at this beautifully, fully renovated home on an acre of land in a great location. check out the flower box built with WOOD THAT IS original to the home! Feel WELCOMED by the cozy patio that is host to a NEW, NEVER BEEN USED, HOT TUB. WANDER inside and ENVISION the gatherings to come. The primary bedroom is BREATHTAKING with the LUXURIOUS VIBE ensuite bathroom. The perfect place to UNWIND after a long day. The kitchen is a DREAM with the OVERSIZED island perfect for dining and entertaining! There is plenty of parking with space for your BOAT or RV. And yet there is still plenty of room to PLAY in the NEWLY fenced yard, with a storage building for your yard tools. Located in close proximity to most of the schools AND all major shopping, just minutes, to BEAUTIFUL LAKE HARTWELL and DOWNTOWN HARTWELL! This PRIME location is easy access to area boat ramps, Hartwell Marina, Paynes Creek Campground, shopping, restaurants, and more. This NEWLY renovated home is ready for YOU to start LIVING YOUR BEST LIFE!
